@context: Demonstrates @var: static variable declaration in hunt files
@blueprint: demo-vars

# Static variables declared here — change test data in one place, not inside steps
@var: {search_query} = autonomous browser testing
@var: {expected_text} = autonomous

1. NAVIGATE to https://duckduckgo.com
2. Fill 'Search' field with '{search_query}'
3. PRESS ENTER
4. VERIFY that '{expected_text}' is present.
5. DONE.
